## ⚙️ 5. Built-in Automated Systems

Lynoria handles settings and themes automatically. You just need to add the built-in sections to your tabs. **Do not skip these**, as users expect to be able to save their configs and change colors!

```lua
-- Personalization (Theme Engine, Live Colors, Save/Delete Themes)
local PersTab = Win:AddTab("Personalization")
PersTab:AddPersonalizationSection()

-- Settings (Config Manager to save all Flags, UI Toggle Keybind)
local SettingsTab = Win:AddTab("Settings")
SettingsTab:AddSettingsSection()
```

