## 🔔 6. Window Controls & Notifications

### Notifications
Lynoria has a built-in notification queue system. Max 3 notifications display at once; extras are queued.

```lua
-- Win:Notify(Title, Message, Type)
-- Type options: "success" (Green), "warning" (Yellow), "error" (Red)
Win:Notify("Auto-Heal", "Successfully healed!", "success")
Win:Notify("Danger", "Admin joined the game!", "error")
```

### Window Methods
You can control the UI programmatically.

```lua
Win:Toggle()   -- Opens or closes the UI (like pressing RightShift)
Win:Minimize() -- Minimizes the UI to just the titlebar (like clicking the yellow traffic light)
Win:Destroy()  -- Completely removes the UI, disconnects all events, deletes the ScreenGui
```

